<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink356">
<l>uḷḷutaṟ kiṉiya maṉṟa celvar</l>
<l>yāṉai piṇitta poṉpuṉai kayiṟṟi</l>
<l>ṉoḷḷeri mēynta curattiṭai</l>
<l>yuḷḷam vāṅkat tantaniṉ kuṇaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Indeed pleasant to think are your virtues given to draw my heart away </l>
<l>from the desert scorched by bright flames, - </l>
<l>like the ropes adorned with gold, </l>
<l>used to tether the elephants of the wealthy. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
